
A simple textarea based editor for
[TiddlySpace](http://tiddlyspace.com) with a small but useful number
of features:

* Support for editing multiple content types
    * Markdown
    * HTML
    * TiddlyWiki text
    * CSS
    * JavaScript
    * Plain Text
* Tag editing with recently used tags displayed
* Loading of a tiddler via URI #fragment
* [Extraclusion](http://edit.tiddlyspace.com/extraclusion)
* Automatic backups to LocalStorage (flakey)

[medit](http://medit.tiddlyspace.com/) is a newer editor for
TiddlySpace with a slightly different feature set.

More info at http://edit.tiddlyspace.com/
